\c 2 Satani anorova Jobho pamuviri wake namaronda 1 Zvino rimwe zuvazve vanakomana vaMwari vakati vachindomira pamberi paJehovha, Satani akasvikawo pakati pavo, akamira pamberi paJehovha. 2 Jehovha akati kuna Satani, "Wabvepik.o?" Satani akapindura Jehovha, akati, "Ndabva pakupota-pota nenyika, napakufamba-famba pairi." 3 Jehovha akati kuna Satani, "Wacherekedza muranda wangu Jobho here?
